org.kiji.schema
Class PutWrapper

java.lang.Object
  org.kiji.schema.KijiDataWrapper<T>
      org.kiji.schema.KeyValueBackedWrapper<Put>
          org.kiji.schema.PutWrapper

public class PutWrapper
extends KeyValueBackedWrapper<Put>

Used by implementations of WrappedDataWriters to wrap data in Puts. Internally wrapped data elements are stored in KeyValues and then aggregated into Puts when getWrapped() is called.

See Also:
KijiDataWrapper
